units were found to be Viet Cong. He

41:08.623 --> 41:21.402
would fit in with the general Vietnamese during 
the day, and during the night then he would be

41:08.623 --> 41:21.402
fighting a different There were also numerous 
instances of where these houseboys or housegirls

