destroying American property and general 
harassment. In retrospect, 24 years after you

41:42.711 --> 41:50.781
served in Vietnam first time, have your thoughts 
and attitudes changed about the war? They had

41:51.588 --> 41:53.210
definitely changed. You've got to remember that 
when I was in the military, and we're talking about

41:53.230 --> 42:05.686
this happened 24, 25 years ago, I was completely 
sold on the military. That was my job. That was my

42:06.847 --> 42:07.909
profession. I was not necessarily brainwashed, 
but I was part of the military establishment at

42:09.090 --> 42:17.121
that time. And as far as I was concerned, we were 
doing the right thing. And to a certain extent, I do

42:20.849 --> 42:27.339
not say that we were necessarily doing the wrong 
thing. In retrospect, yes. However, I think that

42:31.666 --> 42:45.387
we had no part in that war or at very best that it was 
very ill-advised.

42:47.189 --> 42:49.573
We were trying to be part and support a government 
that did not have the people's support, that

42:51.646 --> 43:16.742
abused its position,

